1. *Mašine* u fabrici rade dan i noć. (Machines in the factory work day and night.)
2. Moramo popraviti pokvarene *mašine*. (We need to fix the broken machines.)
3. Proizvodnja je zaustavljena zbog nedostatka *mašina*. (Production has stopped due to a lack of machines.)
4. Ova *mašina* je veoma efikasna i brza. (This machine is very efficient and fast.)
5. Radnik je zadužen za održavanje *mašina*. (The worker is responsible for maintaining the machines.)
6. *Mašine* za pranje sudova su vrlo popularne u domaćinstvima. (Dishwashing machines are very popular in households.)
7. Kupili smo nove *mašine* za šivenje u našoj radionici. (We bought new sewing machines for our workshop.)
8. Tehničar je obučen za popravku različitih vrsta *mašina*. (The technician is trained to repair various types of machines.)
9. Naša firma se bavi iznajmljivanjem građevinskih *mašina*. (Our company rents construction machinery.)
10. Železnica koristi veliki broj *mašina* za održavanje pruga i vozova. (The railway uses a large number of machines to maintain tracks and trains.)